      "slug": "pizza-making-class",
      "tagline": "Stretch dough, top your pie, and fire it yourself.",
      "body": "Our flagship pizza making class brings guests right up to the bench and oven. You will learn how we stretch our dough, build a balanced pie, and work with high-heat live fire without feeling rushed.\n\nEach booking includes dough, toppings, one personal pizza, and a glass of house wine or sparkling lemonade. Great for couples, visitors, and anyone who wants a hands-on dinner plan in Brooklyn.",
